dct_title_s: Geological map of the northern part of Vancouver Island and adjacent coasts; by George M. Dawson.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes 3 insets. Includes lists of "Kwakiool Indian names of places." 1 map: col.; 44 x 81 cm.
